<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Password Changed - ExecStream</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f0f4f8;
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #28a745; /* green to indicate success */
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 28px;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .content h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #28a745;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .content p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 10px 0;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        background-color: #f0f4ff;
        color: #007bff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 16px;
        border: 1px solid #007bff;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      }

      .button:hover {
        background-color: #e0ecff;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.2);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .footer {
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #999;
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>ExecStream</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Password Changed Successfully</h2>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>
          We're confirming that your password was successfully changed. If this
          was you, no further action is needed.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you didn’t make this change, please reset your password immediately
          and contact support.
        </p>
        <a class="button" href="<%= supportUrl %>">Contact Support</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">© <%= year %> ExecStream. All rights reserved.</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
